      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey can u help me out? i'm trying to keep up with the news in pa. there's this new bill being discussed about energy subsidies—basically it's looking to give more money to solar farms but scale back on the subsidies for coal companies. can u give me a quick summary of the pros and cons of this plan? just want to see the different sides of it.",
