      "content": "I get the \"just transition\" thing, but it almost sounds like an excuse to delay progress. If we keep subsidizing coal just to protect everyone, aren't we just wasting tax money on a sunset industry that's holding back the better, cleaner alternatives? Shouldn't the focus be on where the economy is actually going rather than trying to prop up the past?",
